  "purpose": "Wave16 evaluation slicing policy derived from awesome-ai-tools, Prompt-Engineering-Guide, and awesome-ai-agents-e2b. Slices are reporting-only and never mutate routing defaults.",
  "principles": [
    "promote explainability before automation",
    "use slices to compare evidence, not to silently route new behavior",
    "tie every slice to an existing artifact family or a bounded new report",
    "prefer shadow evaluation and operator review over runtime mutation"
